      "position": "Number 8",
      "nationality": "England",
      "blurb": "England No.8 and Quins captain; a powerful one-out ball-carrier with soft hands in tight space who anchors the back row both as a link-man in the wide channels and as a defensive presence over the ball",
      "indexHigh": [
